702442f-a.title: Brooklyn: 6th Street - 7th Avenue
702442f-a.text:
Sixth Street at, adjoining, and west of Seventh Ave. A view of the
Greenwood Baptist Church. In the foreground, are the tracks of the Seventh
Ave., Trolley Line of the B.R.T.
About 1902.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
